  "detailed_description": "Battlegrounds takes the best part of roguelites, tower-defense, strategy and action genres and fuses them to create an enticing gameplay experience with easy to understand mechanics.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703640/extras/d7aa2ee58501292fc5c3cd33ec18ee6c.poster.avif?t=1750114976\" width=590 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703640/extras/d7aa2ee58501292fc5c3cd33ec18ee6c.webm?t=1750114976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>The player must defend his home base from enemy tanks by quickly brainstorming good strategies, unlocking and upgrading machines and making the best use of every new environment present.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703640/extras/8adfc774f6e8d240c47d563e38f82793.poster.avif?t=1750114976\" width=590 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703640/extras/8adfc774f6e8d240c47d563e38f82793.webm?t=1750114976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Highly Replayable</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Awesome soundtracks</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlock and upgrade special vehicles</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore various strategies and playstyles</li></ul>",
